{"tid":1814889,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【懷舊系列】老「果」粉認證？ C朗用iPod Shuffle聽歌成網路熱話","createTime":"2020-01-07T06:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T00:51:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2c05a8055e3f998475082ca9465b4ef15b9f109f","tid":1814889,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗）作為最多社交平台最多粉絲追蹤以及讚好的球星，場內一舉一動，服裝打扮，行為舉止都會成為網上熱話。而今次這位34歲的葡萄牙球星又用一部已經被人遺忘的上世代電子產物成為網上熱話，就是他入場時所用的iPod Shuffle。<br />\n<br />\n在祖雲達斯Facebook專頁公開的相片中，可以看到C朗在入場時正領帶夾着一部iPod Shuffle，而這部iPod Shuffle是蘋果公司於2010年推出的產物，為第4代iPod Shuffle，當年亦是一代潮物，全因它輕巧而且有型的設計，亦有多款顏色選擇，所以不少潮人都會帶上身當飾物。不過，自從iPhone出現，加上串流音樂興起，沒有觸控屏以及僅有4GB容量的iPod Shuffle漸漸被市場淘汰，直至17年蘋果公司宣佈停產。<br />\n<br />\n來到了2020年，莫說是iPod Shuffle，連iPod Touch都已經成為過氣產物，不過大球星C朗仍然使用。難怪有球迷指看到這個畫面，還以為自己回到10年前，而未來更可能因C朗引起一輪iPod Shuffle熱潮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200107/large/1578371923_546c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200107%2Flarge%2F1578371923_546c.jpg&h=223a6dea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200107/large/1578371923_4d36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200107%2Flarge%2F1578371923_4d36.jpg&h=0df18c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200107/FMM2NIKBAGBBNWQWIZYMUE4U34/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200107%2FFMM2NIKBAGBBNWQWIZYMUE4U34%2F&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nM0BU04RHr%2BP31d0xuhNw0M%3D&h=e4574f6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200107%2FFMM2NIKBAGBBNWQWIZYMUE4U34%2F&h=8af6b037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200107/FMM2NIKBAGBBNWQWIZYMUE4U34/</a>"},{"pid":"78a2201ae859e8a43298492